Its looking like release won't happen till Friday at the earliest.  
We're going to let some comparison test crawls that we have running here 
go to completion so we can be more sure the new software works at least 
as the old one did. Grab the download from our crawltools server if you 
want to play with a release candidate: 
http://crawltools.archive.org:8080/cruisecontrol/artifacts/HEAD-heritrix/.
